## Phase 6 — Aggressive, centralised typography

**Single source of truth:** `src/styles/theme.css`. Every font size in the deck (hero slide included) reads from a CSS variable defined there. Nothing else is allowed to declare a font size.

New / updated tokens in `src/styles/theme.css`:

```css
:root {
  /* --- canonical slide typography (edit here to retune all slides) --- */
  --slide-text-h2: 4.5rem;       /* was --font-size-h2: 3.5rem */
  --slide-text-body: 2rem;       /* was --slide-text-normal: 1.35rem */
  --slide-text-code: 1.25rem;    /* was --font-size-code: 0.82–0.85rem (inline) */

  /* --- title-slide hero calibration (edit here to retune the title slide) --- */
  --hero-title-size: 94px;
  --hero-tagline-size: 56px;
  --hero-speaker-size: 38px;
  --hero-badge-size: 34px;

  /* --- chrome badge sizes --- */
  --chrome-badge-size: 28px;
  --chrome-logo-width: 364px;

  /* aliases for backwards compatibility during migration (remove at end of phase 6) */
  --font-size-h2: var(--slide-text-h2);
  --slide-text-normal: var(--slide-text-body);
  --font-size-code: var(--slide-text-code);
}
```

Migration steps:
1. Add the new tokens to `src/styles/theme.css`.
2. Replace every hit of `style={{ '--font-size-code': '0.82rem' }}` / `'0.85rem'` on slides (grep shows 4 slides: `MetaSkillsSlide`, `WarcraftFunSlide`, `AutoApproveHookSlide`, `AgentWorkflowSlide`, `SkillsActivatorSlide`, `AgentTracesSlide`) with plain CodeBlock usage — no inline style.
3. Replace every hardcoded `fontSize` inline attribute on SVG text (in `EveryOrgRightNowSlide`, `InceptionPatternsSlide`, `AIInnovatorCurveSlide`) with `style={{ fontSize: 'var(--slide-text-body)' }}` or a new token `--svg-label-size` if SVG needs its own scale.
4. Replace hero-slide hardcoded px in `src/styles/slides.css` with the `--hero-*` variables.
5. Once every slide reads from tokens, drop the backwards-compat aliases and rename old references.

**Result:** every font size in the deck can be retuned by editing **one file** (`src/styles/theme.css`). This is explicitly what the user asked for.

Files touched:
- `src/styles/theme.css` (new tokens, aliases)
- `src/styles/slides.css` (swap hero hardcoded px for vars)
- All 6 code-block slides listed above (remove inline `--font-size-code`)
- 3 data-viz slides (swap inline SVG fontSize for var)
- `src/slides/TitleSlide.tsx` (no content change; style lives in CSS)

